{"tid":1719100,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"攻打大學係警甴圍魏救趙既方法","createTime":"2019-11-14T04:22:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T04:26:41.000Z","uid":61886,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5509da2874911cf05f43f7debb0a0093ba0de900","tid":1719100,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T04:22:02.000Z","msg":"啱啱屙屎果既<br />\n諗咗一諗今個星期警察嘅部署<br />\n當多個思考既角度<br />\n<br />\n11.11 早上 黎明行動<br />\n係近兩個月首次大型不合作運動<br />\n令鐵路同道路都癱瘓<br />\n同時 民意反彈冇之前塞鐵果時咁勁<br />\n<br />\n11.11 中午<br />\n警察開始攻打中大<br />\n估計原因：<br />\n1. 保護吐露港同大學站路軌<br />\n2. 限制中大前線活動範圍 不能離開中大<br />\n3. 一舉攻入中大 大規模搜捕<br />\n<br />\n意料不到<br />\n中大全力反抗<br />\n變相雙方對峙及互有攻守<br />\n令黎明行動人手減少<br />\n<br />\n係警察圍魏救趙嘅手段<br />\n所救既趙 就係香港既經濟 <br />\n即係大眾可唔可以返工<br />\n<br />\n11.11 晚上 18區開花<br />\n到我哋圍魏救趙<br />\n我哋救既係中大嘅手足<br />\n<br />\n個故事發展大約係咁樣<br />\n<br />\n咁引申到嘅結論係<br />\n1. 黎明行動直擊港共春袋<br />\n2. 18區開花係圍魏救趙嘅手段，而非主線<br />\n3. 黎明行動係最重要<br />\n4. 當有事發生，需要百方支援<br />\n5. 如冇事發生，請全力黎明行動<br />\n<br />\n1115 黎明行動 0600見"},{"pid":"3ce9e06c210bae3dcfa11017b9558c00e6a710aa","tid":1719100,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T04:24:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"20cb7c222ecb23d550f41a10c7fce9b76d75c804","tid":1719100,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T04:25:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">［文宣入！］返工搭鐵受襲、催淚彈影響健康、女學生返學俾狗捉，<strong>請文宣製圖向怕死嘅打工仔、家長、學生宣傳三罷</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n林鄭連續兩日叫大家唔好罷工罷課，證明罷工罷課係佢春袋，然而差佬不斷製造罷工罷課條件，文宣請行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請文宣組以<span style=\"color: red;\">黑警返工時間突襲旺角站無差別襲擊勤力返工人士</span>、<span style=\"color: gold;\">中午中環射催淚彈</span>、<span style=\"color: red;\">警察街上捉返學嘅女學生</span>、<span style=\"color: gold;\">以及警察話上堂等於非法集結</span>，做罷工罷課文宣圖<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">警告堅持要返工返學嘅人，即將面對惡犬強姦殺人滅口嘅危險，在網上廣傳！</span><br />\n<blockquote> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8oPyZO5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8oPyZO5.jpg&h=3f965005&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FJQN4pc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFJQN4pc.jpg&h=87289d57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/abpOQ16.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FabpOQ16.png&h=1a9ab24c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zQHwOww.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzQHwOww.jpg&h=056adf34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JerhLyH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJerhLyH.png&h=a8e9db0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1713400\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1713400</a>"},{"pid":"d626d2bff72e6e2fb0efde805a49c7137f321ad6","tid":1719100,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T04:26:41.000Z","msg":"推"}]}